  "text": "The OCSVM algorithm in this paper is designed to detect potential attacks in multiple Modbus data packets; the function code of Modbus protocol is extracted from the communication data, which represents a communication operation The data processed by OCSVM are required to have the same dimensions. In this paper, different numbers of Modbus function code sequences are converted into the vector with the same length on the basis of our previous research [CITATION_1] .",
